_sText:
I made this in about an hour. i dont expect you to favourite it or put it up on your server. I just wanted to show that a very simple layout, and a map made with with minimal effort can be better looking and more fun to play than the dev texture GG map you've been working on all week. 

unzip the map file (.bsp) into C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\XXXXXXX_XXXX\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps
